on at the corotation resonance, but can be stabilized by modest disc\nmagnetic fields. The overstable oscillation modes studied in this paper have\ncharacteristic properties that make them possible candidates for the\nquasi-periodic oscillations observed in X-ray binaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2012 20:56:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Mar 2012 19:57:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-05-28"}
