 bars), but the penetration\ndepth varies with the atmospheric opacity. The total dissipated Ohmic power\nincreases steeply with the strength of the irradiating flux and the dissipation\ndepth recedes into the atmosphere, favoring radius inflation in the most\nirradiated objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2012 21:08:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Mar 2012 17:18:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
