entricities. As the timespan of timing data increases,\ndynamical fits may allow detailed constraints on the systems' architectures,\neven in cases for which high-precision Doppler follow-up is impractical.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2012 23:36:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Apr 2012 19:35:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
